{"tid":1697091,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"抗爭5個月，覺得心很累嘅入一入黎...","createTime":"2019-11-06T15:16:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T17:25:57.000Z","uid":200121,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a569c79185741f0a9d98d20d84dcfc0f9fe64214","tid":1697091,"uid":200121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:16:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bxCDU9i2piU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbxCDU9i2piU&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNbY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=528b7c65\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bxCDU9i2piU</a><br />\n<br />\n各位手足大家好！<br />\n我地哩場運動經歷左就快五個月<br />\n唔知係乜嘢驅使大家堅持到哩一刻，但係我相信我地都係為左一份信念而企埋一齊！<br />\n面對社會上種種嘅不公、官員嘅厚顏無恥、黑警嘅暴力...<br />\n好似次次發完夢都解決唔到咁<br />\n<br />\n我有班基督徒朋友，佢哋好好咁作左首歌，去為大家打打氣<br />\n<strong>無論你地係咪基督徒都好，都請你地禁入去聽聽首歌</strong><br />\n入面紀錄嗮我地五個月黎，最令香港人深刻嘅種種片段<br />\n希望大家覺得灰心嘅時候，都唔好放棄我地堅持左五個月嘅信念<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>亦都好想讓大家知道，香港有班唔係耶L嘅基督徒一直同大家並肩作戰！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命！<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可！</span>"},{"pid":"47ed44d86daca068b6113a3c1d12caf5954e40c8","tid":1697091,"uid":175159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:54:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jxeurey.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjxeurey.jpg&h=8370b0df&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NV4qJ1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNV4qJ1d.jpg&h=ba0393f4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p4xLJ1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp4xLJ1e.jpg&h=aedc1121&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6156a7065cb63c38bc444089e1f61bb4a96ab99c","tid":1697091,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T17:25:57.000Z","msg":"[重新整合]11.10 7區開花！ 11.11全港3罷！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697199\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1697199</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}